        {
          "heading": "样例说明",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在第一个例子中，$\\texttt{Genos}$ 可以在一秒钟就把这行珠子全部移走。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在第二个例子中，$\\texttt{Genos}$ 一次只能移走一个珠子，所以移走三个珠子花费他三秒。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "在第三个例子中，为了达到 $2$ 秒的最快时间，先移除回文串 $\\texttt{4 4}$,再移除回文串 $\\texttt{1 2 3 2 1}$。",
              "depth": 1
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "题解",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "题意：从一个序列中每次取出一个回文串，求最少取几次（取出后两端外的数会相接）",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "设 \\( dp[i][j] \\) 为在 \\([i, j]\\) 的区间内最少的花费",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "显然",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\[\\begin{cases}\ndp[i][i] = 1 \\\\\ndp[i][i+1] = 1 \\quad (a[i] = a[i+1]) \\\\\ndp[i][i+1] = 2 \\quad (a[i] \\neq a[i+1])\n\\end{cases}\\]",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "于是可以推出转移方程：",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "math",
          "latex": "\\[\\begin{cases}\ndp[i][j] = dp[i+1][j-1] \\quad (a[i] = a[j]) \\\\\ndp[i][j] = \\min_{k=i}^{j-1} dp[i][k] + dp[k+1][j]\n\\end{cases}\\]",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "这里唯一需要注意的点是：$dp[i][j] = dp[i+1][j-1] \\quad (a[i] = a[j])$ 的正确性。",
          "depth": 1
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "下意识会认为是先把 $(i +1,j -1)$ 消掉再消除 $a[i]$ 和 $a[j]$，难道答案要再 $+1$ 吗？",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "但实际上，我们可以 <strong>“借用”</strong> 给中间区间 $[i+1, j-1]$ 的最后一次消除过程。",
          "depth": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "因此，消除 $[i, j]$ 的代价等于消除 $[i+1, j-1]$ 的代价，不需要 $+1$。",
          "depth": 2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "代码",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "code",
          "lang": "cpp",
          "code": "int a[505], dp[505][505];\nvoid solve(int CASE)\n{\n\tint n; cin >> n;\n\tfa(i, 1, n)cin >> a[i];\n\tfa(i, 1, n)fa(j, 1, n)dp[i][j] = INF;\n\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tdp[i][i] = 1;\n\t\tif (i != n) {\n\t\t\tif (a[i] == a[i + 1])dp[i][i + 1] = 1;\n\t\t\telse dp[i][i + 1] = 2;\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\tfa(len, 3, n)\n\t\tfa(i, 1, n) {\n\t\tint j = i + len - 1;\n\t\tif (j > n)break;\n\t\tif (a[i] == a[j])\n\t\t\tdp[i][j] = dp[i + 1][j - 1];\n\t\tfa(k, i, j - 1)\n\t\t\tdp[i][j] = min(dp[i][j], dp[i][k] + dp[k + 1][j]);\n\t}\n\tcout << dp[1][n] << endl;\n\treturn;\n}",
          "depth": 1
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
